= Usage =
The '''{{tl|Golf18}}''' template creates a table header for an 18-hole [[golf course]] scorecard. Additional rows are added to the table to show par for each hole, to show the hole [[golf handicap|handicaps]] and to show the yardages for each [[teeing ground|tee]]. The set of templates used to create a golf scorecard are:

